          <span>${c.address}</span><br/>
          <a href="tel:${c.phone}" style="text-decoration:none">â˜ï¸ ${c.phone}</a>
        </div>`
      );
      markers.set(c.id, m);
      bounds.push([c.lat, c.lng]);
